Therion (Octopath Traveler)
Weapon type: Dagger
Crystal Color: Black
Spheres: A C E

Skill 1: HP Thief
 1-hit Melee BRV+HP Attack.
 Restores HP to self based on HP damage dealt (20%).
 Uses: 6
15cp: Stinging Dagger
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases HP recovered based on HP damage dealt (+5%)
 +Triggers ability a second time if HP is above 50% after initial use
c.55: HP Thief Extend
 +Adds 1 use
 +Becomes a 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice
 +Grants BRV to self based on HP damage dealt after first HP attack (50%)
 +Grants BRV to self based on TOTAL HP damage dealt after second HP attack (20%)
 +Extends duration of existing [Fleetfoot] by 1 turn
 +Extends duration of all self buffs by 1 turn when breaking/attacking a broken target

Skill 2: Wildfire
 Gain BRV based on ATK (100%)
 1-hit Fire Magic BRV attack.
 Deals increased BRV damage when attacking an enemy's weakness (+50%).
 Grants [Fleetfoot] to self for 2 turns.
 Uses: 4
35cp: Arcane Knife
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Improves BRV gain based on ATK (+40%)
 Extends base duration of [Fleetfoot] by 2 turns
 +Triggers ability a second time if HP is above 50% after initial use
c.60: Wildfire Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Becomes a 4-hit Fire Magic BRV+HP attack
 +Improves BRV gain based on ATK (+60%)
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
 
[Fleetfoot]: Fire Enchant (40%)
             ATK Up (30%), SPD Up (20%), Evasion Up (40%)
             HP Damage Taken Up (30%)
 
EX: Trickster's Dagger
 +Equips EX ability Aeber's Reckoning
Inflicts BREAK on all targets (unless already BROKEN) 
4-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack.
Deals 100% HP damage to all targets.
BRV damage is also modified by SPD (BRV Damage * 0.3 SPD)
 Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Aeber's Reckoning by 20%
  -LB3: Inflicts Fire Resistance Down on all targets for 6 turns
 EX+: Greatly increases BRV potency
      Allows for 120% Stolen BRV Overflow
      Triggers ability a second time if HP is above 50% after initial use
      BRV Attack becomes BRV Attack+ when HP is below 50%
      HP Attack becomes HP Attack+ when HP is below 50%
      BRV Attack becomes BRV Attack++ when HP is above 50%
      HP Attack becomes HP Attack++ when HP is above 50%
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (50%) and Max BRV (60%)
  -LB2: At Quest Start:
        -Grants [Fleetfoot] to self for 4 turns
        -Fills Recast Gauge to MAX
  -LB3: Becomes a 6-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack
        Allows for 150% Stolen BRV Overflow
        Adds the following effect to [Fleetfoot]:
         While [Fleetfoot] is active
         -Nullifies Action Delay when inflicting BREAK, grants 1 extra turn
         -Extra turn does not increase turn count
         -Cannot trigger an additional turn during extra turn

BRV Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV attack.
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
            Grants BRV to self based on HP damage dealt (20%).
BRV Attack++: 4-hit Melee BRV attack.          
HP Attack++: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.
             Grants BRV to self based on HP damage dealt after both HP attacks (20%).

LD: Skybreaker
 +Equips LD ability Shackle Foe
6-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack.
Deals 50% splash HP damage to non-targets.
Allows for 180% Stolen BRV Overflow.
Inflicts [Insult to Injury] on all targets for 4 turns.
Inflicts Fire Resistance Down on all targets for 6 turns.
 Uses: 2
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (20%) and SPD (10%)
        Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Raises own ATK (20%) and SPD (10%)
        Extends base duration of [Insult to Injury] by 4 turns
  -LB3: Raises own ATK (20%) and SPD (10%)
        Adds 1 use
Board Passive: LD Extend
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Triggers ability a second time if HP is above 50% after initial use

[Insult to Injury]: BRV Damage Dealt Down (50%)
                    Weakness BRV Damage Taken Up (60%)
                    BREAK/BROKEN BRV Damage Taken Up (40%)
